Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然买得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希就知道不停地往筐里放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…滑了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没伤着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…鸡蛋碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  待会儿再买就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我赔钱给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是好大的风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是第一阵春风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吹春香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:25.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（春香的读音于春风相近）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笑话真冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋的钱你会出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:40.13,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第10碗  舍华求实的年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种笑话还真受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来就好笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子你平时都看什么节目？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这丫头只知道看新闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？那么死板怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且新闻有什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说社会上发生的各种事都很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社会上的…是指案件啊事故什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是活动或体育新闻之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  快完事回来说些丰富多彩的新闻听听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们养猫了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  偶尔会跑来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是四楼  怎么爬到阳台上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是坐电梯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是在骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子上厕所好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？想这么玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩？指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  要钻进被炉里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘拿手帕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子是多么…多么的可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是淳子转世吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家没死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的蜜柑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小气干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…今天请各位光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有重要的事情要宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天会让身边的蠢货们变得活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货们是指谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夏奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  当然是真希你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  我们为了能迅速地吐蠢货们的槽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须对此进行练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家的小千秋到底接受了怎样的教育啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面跟着我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一亿日元而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才一亿日元而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是要吐在什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞虾米啊  你这蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞虾米啊  你这蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁吐的槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真希  大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋她们开始练吐槽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这不是好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  真希你觉得没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们不带你一起练习吐槽  就当你是白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:06:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  千秋用文件夹把蠢货和正常人分得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有家人用的文件夹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有春香享有桌面上快捷方式的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么  千秋  电脑拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正忙着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些  夏奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才看了看春香买的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚饭应该是烤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉…我想吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是前些天不是刚吃过牛肉火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉…我想吃烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  烤肉不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…烤好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～牛舌真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  鸡软骨  鸡软骨也烤好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有…里脊  里脊也不能没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  赏花啊  不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏花？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  是里～脊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花现在还是花苞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对啦  是里脊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得像花苞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花苞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来啦  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我跟你说  刚才千秋把里脊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  蠢货！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  小心感冒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  千秋怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋说想去赏花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏花？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是赏花  不如说是去看花苞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然天气还很冷…要去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是期待啊  里脊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  错了  是赏花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得  也叫上冬木吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好啊  吃完饭我过去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给人家添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不会去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬木说他要去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了  那就按人数准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  洗澡水烧好了  你去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣啊  去吧  我也去我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在赏花是不是早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是夏奈提议的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然像她的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在早了点怎么都不劝劝她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要去赏花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花都还没开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？那也能叫赏花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊  烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？不是赏花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啥不好  边赏花边烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说大家一起去赏花的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏花？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是早了点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  总之来赏花吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我已经有安排了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！比赏花还重要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…要模拟考…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你就天天对着重要的模拟考睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  藤冈  你明天有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…明天的话  嗯  有空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然不知道是要干什么…我就打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个好人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位早！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都该知道  赏花的关键是占个好位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  采购就更不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我想趁现在决定各自的分工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  阿真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来是没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  可以的话我来占位置好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去占位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是采购比较有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去采购算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干什么好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  三个男生去占位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？三个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛干嘛  别犹豫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那内田  你来负责采购了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:03.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说夏奈  可以买很多零食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等下在樱花树下见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待各位的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她们还真是够精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样才讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样才舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人安心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:12:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么了  过来帮忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说光吃烤肉太单调的不是真希你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  我来帮忙就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  围裙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  合适吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副扮相怎么会合适嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  夏奈都这么吩咐了也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你是最近才搬来这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  你跟千秋是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一堆无关的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当的便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  我这么会买东西还真是麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会有需要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫罐头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你边赏花边吃猫罐头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  全部集齐的话可以拼成房子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一盒里只有一个零件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩给我适可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希你没事吧  有没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  拿这个擦擦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是夏奈她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了…哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要赏花吗  也加我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不过这种事情还是要问问女孩子的意见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？呃…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错吧…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就选这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生在这方面的眼光还是差些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  问了个奇怪问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我看起来像男孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来  果汁还有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须快点去夏奈她们那儿…便当也还…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  没关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来尝尝这特制木天蓼果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学她们好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道带TS过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么  TS是什么的缩写？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Tandem Screen{\r}\N上下屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬马  藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有的事  不是第一批吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一天也不会有第二批人来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看  全部集齐的话能拼个房子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～其它还买什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫粮？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  春香姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  她还没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该快来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道已经在那边烤上肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  怎么想也不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学她真有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏奈  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么晚啊  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来  过来一起喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来嘛…夏奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那边有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要商量一下接下来怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要走了  之后再喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:16:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  给你礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？你都干什么去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去迟了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指望你也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来  吉野拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是果汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  都有什么味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故将有五危
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:18:02.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（出自孙子兵法「九变第八」）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:17:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必死可杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必生可虏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忿速可侮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廉洁可辱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱民可烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:15.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射将先射马！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不冷吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  差不多该去赏花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是千秋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  为你的到来干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢…就蒸了一下…蒸的东西就这样…就这样喷出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊  真的好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  千秋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  不管是谁赶紧回来个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  现在是世界上最长且最让人难耐的三分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我用自己的零用钱买的  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶啊  突然就下起雨来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的  都成落汤鸡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上天气预报不是说过会下雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没带伞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧换衣服吧  我给你放洗澡水去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须死在这里  不能让你再活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  要杀就动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死你的前未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么你要背叛组织
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  再过十分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是暖身子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完这个就去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要  哪种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你们两个怎么都在吃泡面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就该吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香要吃吗  很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…那我也吃一点儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:20.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:20.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:29.56,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:29.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:38.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:38.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:47.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:47.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:58.87,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:58.87,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:07.75,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:07.75,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:16.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:16.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:28.13,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:28.13,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗鼻子时候有被呛到的经历吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.13,0:23:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为鼻液和水的浓度不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用生理盐水洗的话就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着只要按住半边鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:46.12,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(250,0)}第11碗  「果然不妙了」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用鼻子吸水  然后把流到嘴里的水吐出来  就通畅了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就是如何习惯了  加油哦
